snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's STARS | Trailer
snippet.description:
First Trailer for Five Nights at Freddy's STARS!
| Part of Kane Carter's BMC Creator Showcase

Five Nights at Freddy’s STARS it’s an Online Multiplayer FNaF fangame, play with up to 4 players and try to get the highest score to win!.
Featuring a lot of characters from the original games, this game tries to be a fun experience for everyone!.

Releasing this Spring!
Follow Now on Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/FNAFSTARS/606034
